    - Every action flows through Lucidia's memory spine \'97 zero context-switching                                                                                                                            \
  2. \cf4 RoadTrip\cf2  \'97 Pick up your passengers. They never forget the ride.                                                                                                                                        \
    - 27 named agents across 7 divisions with distinct personalities and voices                                                                                                                             \
    - Persistent memory across days, weeks, months \'97 sessions are dead                                                                                                                                      \
    - Three memory layers: Hot (instant), Warm (consolidated insights), Cold (full archive)                                                                                                                 \
    - Natural language triggers choreograph multi-agent collaboration                                                                                                                                       \
    - Convoy Radio mode \'97 agents work audibly in the background while you focus                                                                                                                             \
